Centre pour la Sécurité de l'IA (CeSIA)
https://www.securite-ia.fr/

CeSIA is a french non profit dedicated to education and reaserach on the challenges of Artificial Intelligence. It hosts weekly meetups in Paris, teaches ai safety at top french universities and international ai safety bootcamps. It is open to volunteers joining.
